常灵活。我觉得不难，但辅导我的女儿，她就是不会。”张小强教授非常纳闷，为什么当年自己学习时一点不费力，如今女儿就不一样了?并在自己的朋友圈吐槽：这应该是很多大学老师的无奈。 “一辅导作业，鸡飞狗跳;不辅导作业，父慈子孝。”张教授表示，现在女儿即将面对中考，目前正是冲刺阶段，希望女儿能保持好的心理状态，考出理想的成绩。 虽然这位教授的应对非常可爱，使其在网上成为热搜，但事件背后还是有疑问：既有印象中都是觉得高学历家长教育孩子更应该有一手，然而本新闻中对初中生女儿的教育却束手无策，还吐槽到这是很多大学老师的痛，为什么会产生这样的偏差？教育应如何对症下药？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3YPDkP/3zO5wEAMaCDY1MDY3NTQ4IM7T1oUGMAY4nQJAFnIJNDYyNTQ2Njc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"303 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e63172978d4525489670d17271f035e0_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1622632388.497508","card_id":"Q_266593795","target":{"id":266593795,"title":"你吃过最绝望的食物是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/266593795","type":"question","created":1517594961,"answer_count":1267,"follower_count":3580,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,617,19402],"comment_count":29,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"Quora 上面看到的问题，感觉很有意思"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3YPDkP/3zO5wEAMaCDIxMDY5NzA4INHS0tMFMB04/BtAF3IJMjY2NTkzNzk1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"298 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a75e5b23f3753dd7dbe87164a6c7ea4_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1622632388.4979186","card_id":"Q_462115454","target":{"id":462115454,"title":"iPhone 12 已经降了超过 1400 元了，618 还会再降吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/462115454","type":"question","created":1622301099,"answer_count":67,"follower_count":148,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[520,25409,105508,221195,449867],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"今天iphone价格跳的有点猛，还会再降吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3YPDkP/3zO5wEAMaCDY0OTcxNzYzIKuzyYU